name: Secrets of the Enchanted Forest V2

metadata.name: Let the magic begin!
metadata.description:
Meet the Queen of Enchanted Forest. She is the keeper of a key to the door that leads there. Thalia- the curious owl, wanted to get inside and uncover the mysteries of the woods. Curious to know what is waiting behind the door?.. Dive into the fairy atmosphere, feel a warm touch of wind and enjoy travelling. Let Talia guide you through the forest revealing secrets as you go. By the way, she has one herself..

This art took me 39 hours to draw.
1/1  4724*6300px 400dpi
